ns1:contractData.ns1:descriptionOfContractRequirement:
THE PURPOSE OF MODIFICATION P00103 TO THE HRACCESS INDEFINITE DELIVERY INDEFINITE QUANTITY (IDIQ) CONTRACT HSTS01-08-D-HRM010 IS TO:

(A)  EXERCISE OPTION PERIOD FIVE (5) EFFECTIVE JANUARY 2, 2014 THROUGH JANUARY 1, 2015.

(B)  CORRECT THE AWARD FEE ASSOCIATED WITH CLINS 6002 "RECRUITMENT ACTIVITIES," 6019 "NATIONAL&NATURAL DISASTER HELP DESK," AND CLIN 6023 "FIXED PRICE AWARD FEE" TO ACCURATELY REFLECT THE IDENTIFIED PERCENTAGE OF THE ASSOCIATED CLINS CURRENT VALUE;

(C)  RENAME CLIN SERIES XX15AC "SF-52&BENEFITS PROCESSING (PASS)" AND DECREASE THE ASSOCIATED QUANTITY;

(D)  RE-ALLOCATE FUNDING FROM CLIN 6022 "TRAVEL" TO NEWLY CREATED SUB-CLIN 6022A "OTHER ALLOWABLE DIRECT COSTS (ODCS);"

(E)  INCORPORATE DATA ITEM DESCRIPTION (DID) FOR INTERNAL USE SOFTWARE COSTS - PHASE REPORT;

(F)  UPDATE SECTION 6  OF THE STATEMENT OF WORK (SOW) "HELP DESK" FOR CLIN SERIES XX18 TO INCLUDE TRANSPORTATION OFFICER PERFORMANCE SYSTEM (TOPS) AND ANNUAL PROFICIENCY REVIEW (APR) SUPPORT;

(G)  ADD CLINS 6018B "TOPS / APR SUPPORT" AND 6018B-1 "TOPS / APR SUPPORT CONTRACT CHANGE COSTS;" AND

(H)  UPDATE THE CONTRACT.
